lmm_stripe_offset:  1&lt;br/&gt;
	obdidx		 objid		 objid		 group&lt;br/&gt;
	     1	         30476	       0x770c	             0&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; replay-single test_90: @@@@@@ FAIL: wrong stripe: f0, uuid: lustre-OST0000_UUID &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: replay-single 90&lt;/p&gt;</description>
